[[Image:Homemade_Flan.jpg|thumb]]

'''焦糖'''，把[[糖|糖]]煮到[[攝氏|攝氏]]170℃时焦糖化产生的物质。焦糖加入[[沸水|沸水]]煮化，即是[[液態|液態]]焦糖，可以用來泡[[咖啡|咖啡]]或做[[布丁|布丁]]。焦糖常被用在制作甜点上，它可以为糕点和甜点提供一种填补糖果或巧克力的风味，或加于[[冰淇淋|冰淇淋]]和[[蛋奶冻|蛋奶冻]]上。或作為[[食物|食物]][[黑色素|黑色素]]，如可乐之类的饮料使用焦糖着色，而且它也被用作食品[[着色剂|着色剂]]，它也是[[威士忌|威士忌]]行业唯一允许使用的[[添加剂|添加剂]]。而牛奶糖的做法是把[[黃油|奶油]]、[[牛奶|牛奶]]和糖一起煮到攝氏120度。

==糖色==
糖色，俗稱「醬色」，加入植物性食用油和砂糖熱炒後的產物，也可作為食品添加物，如可樂、麵包等增色劑，或用於紅燒料理，成本比[[老抽|老抽]]低廉，而且沒有[[醬油|醬油]]的鹹味。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/supplement/paper/721580|date=2013-10-13|title=〈看g道評味道〉炒出糖色 免加色素|accessdate=2016-05-18|author=梁瓊白|publisher=[[自由時報|自由時報]]|archive-date=2018-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180201135146/http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/supplement/paper/721580|dead-url=no}}</ref>但若是過量食用糖類，有「糖中毒」的危險性<ref>{{cite book|date=2014-05-07|origyear=2014|author2=楊詠婷（譯者）|title= 《2週間で効果がでる白澤式ケトン食事法》|trans-title=《糖中毒，當然會三高！》| author=白澤卓二|publisher=方舟文化|pages= 192頁|isbn=978-9869058605}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.businesstoday.com.tw/article-content-80731-109527 |title= 你以為只有毒品會慢慢上癮嗎? |date= 2014-08-01 |publisher= 今周刊 |access-date= 2016-05-19 |archive-date= 2020-11-01 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201101102821/http://www.businesstoday.com.tw/article-content-80731-109527 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name="Nestler">{{cite journal | author = Robison AJ, Nestler EJ | title = Transcriptional and epigenetic mechanisms of addiction | journal = Nat. Rev. Neurosci. | volume = 12 | issue = 11 | pages = 623–637 |date=November 2011  | pmid = 21989194 | pmc = 3272277 | doi = 10.1038/nrn3111 | quote = ΔFosB has been linked directly to several addiction-related behaviors ...  Importantly, genetic or viral overexpression of ΔJunD, a dominant negative mutant of JunD which antagonizes ΔFosB- and other AP-1-mediated transcriptional activity, in the NAc or OFC blocks these key effects of drug exposure14,22–24. This indicates that ΔFosB is both necessary and sufficient for many of the changes wrought in the brain by chronic drug exposure. ΔFosB is also induced in D1-type NAc MSNs by chronic consumption of several natural rewards, including sucrose, high fat food, sex, wheel running, where it promotes that consumption14,26–30. This implicates ΔFosB in the regulation of natural rewards under normal conditions and perhaps during pathological addictive-like states. }}</ref><ref name="Natural and drug addictions">{{cite journal | author = Olsen CM | title = Natural rewards, neuroplasticity, and non-drug addictions | journal = Neuropharmacology | volume = 61 | issue = 7 | pages = 1109–22 |date=December 2011  | pmid = 21459101 | pmc = 3139704 | doi = 10.1016/j.neuropharm.2011.03.010 | url = }}</ref><ref name="Avena-Rada-Hoebel">{{cite journal | last1 = Avena | first1 = Nicole M. | last2 = Rada | first2 = Pedro | last3 = Hoebel | first3 = Bartley G. | year = 2008 | title = Evidence for sugar addiction: Behavioral and neurochemical effects of intermittent, excessive sugar intake | journal = Neuroscience & Biobehavioral Reviews | volume = 32 | issue = 1| pages = 20–39 | pmc=2235907 | pmid=17617461 | doi=10.1016/j.neubiorev.2007.04.019}}</ref>。

另外，化學製備，以[[4-甲基咪唑|4-甲基咪唑]]為主的[[焦糖色素|焦糖色素]]（IARC第2B類致癌物質）。

